    noria:alarmSeverity <Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Informational> .

# Example of a change request impacting a service
<https://w3id.org/noria/changerequest/CR-20240425-002> noria:changeRequestImpact <https://w3id.org/noria/service/InternalNetworkConnectivity> .

# Example of a corporate user identifier
